  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Marketing Manager",
  "description": "<h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Conduct garment design research to identify trends, fabrics, colors, and styles aligned with buyer and market demands</p></li><li><p>Develop and oversee the design and product development process, from concept to final presentation</p></li><li><p>Review, evaluate, and refine garment designs to ensure quality, fit, cost efficiency, and production feasibility</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with sampling, merchandising, and production teams to ensure designs are accurately executed</p></li><li><p>Prepare and organize professional design presentations for buyers</p></li><li><p>Present collections and design concepts to international buyers, including those from the US</p></li><li><p>Incorporate buyer feedback into design revisions and future collections</p></li><li><p>Ensure all designs comply with buyer specifications, quality standards, and timelines</p></li><li>Stay updated on global fashion trends and competitor activity</li></ul><p><strong>Pre-requisites</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s Degree or Diploma in Marketing, Fashion Design, Apparel Design, or a related field</li><li>Minimum 5 years of experience in the garment or apparel industry, preferably in a managerial or senior design role</li><li>Strong expertise and hands-on experience in garment design and development</li><li>Proven ability in design research, product development, and presentation</li><li>Excellent understanding of fabrics, trims, garment construction, and costing</li><li>Experience presenting to international buyers is highly preferred</li><li>Strong communication and coordination skills</li><li>Ability to manage multiple styles and deadlines simultaneously</li><li>Proficiency in design and presentation tools (e.g., Adobe Illustrator, Photoshop, PowerPoint)</li><li>Willing to travel overseas for work</li></ul><p>Interested applicants are welcome to submit your MS Word resume to career@oneconsulting-global.sg</p><p>EA Personnel R1107675</p><p>Agency no. 07C3676</p>",
